feedback.text: My overall experience has been life easier and more helpful when I need to get back to certain websites or documents. It's a overall trusted so far and great software to use for your browsers.
The benefits are that its easy to sell online not that much work. If someone needs to buy something they can just get it here and its incredibly useful.

Great customer service and support. They are always there to help with any issues. The community is very active and help each other out. I have the sense that great things are coming in the near future.
